**Address Mapping Analysis: Xã Cam Phước Tây, Khánh Hòa**

Alright, let's break down this address: "Xã Cam Phước Tây, Huyện Cam Lâm, Tỉnh Khánh Hòa".  My initial task is to identify the old administrative units: "Xã Cam Phước Tây" (ward), "Huyện Cam Lâm" (district, though we're ignoring districts in this task), and "Tỉnh Khánh Hòa" (province).

First, I checked for any province name changes in "60-NQ/TW". Thankfully, Khánh Hòa remains Khánh Hòa, so that simplifies things.

Now, the crucial step: I dove into the "Other resolutions" focusing on Khánh Hòa.  I immediately homed in on "1667/NQ-UBTVQH15: Sắp xếp các đơn vị hành chính cấp xã của tỉnh Khánh Hòa".  And bingo! Line 21 explicitly states that "Xã Cam Phước Tây" is merged to form "Xã Cam An" along with parts of Cam An Bắc and Cam An Nam.  That's the key.

This means I can confidently map "Xã Cam Phước Tây" to the new "Xã Cam An."  I validated this against the "New Wards" list, and sure enough, there it is: {"ward_code":"22465","ward_name":"Xã Cam An","province_name":"Tỉnh Khánh Hòa"}.  Perfect match!

My confidence in this mapping is high because of the explicit mention in the resolution.  The citation will be: "1667/NQ-UBTVQH15: Sắp xếp các đơn vị hành chính cấp xã của tỉnh Khánh Hòa", line "21. This should provide all the necessary information for a definitive answer.
